    "intro": "Interpretation asks what the text means — moving from observation (what does it say?) to the author's intent in his ancient context and the canonical weight it carries. The movements below follow the chapter's argument across its five distinct pericopes. Where Hebrew lexical data sharpens the English, a brief note follows the exposition as supplement.",
